originalText.text:
The pre-K program was great. I have twin daughters and they were in two different classes. Throughout the year, the staff was amazing..... passionate, caring, and professional teachers.

Many thanks to Ms. Lang, Ms. Toomey, Ms. Schawlow, Ms. Lugo, Ms. Mena, Ms. Melendez, and the wonderful principal Mr. Green. We trusted our kids with the staff and we truly had a great year with them.
